# Panda PHP

## 路由
```
Router::get('/foo/:bar', function ($request) {
    echo 'param "bar" is ', $requset->params('bar'), '<br>';
    echo 'query "query" is ', $requset->params('query', 'nothing'), '<br>';
});
```

## 中间件
```
Router::get('/foo',
    function ($request) {
        echo "I'm middleware!";
    },
    function ($request) {
        echo 'GET /foo'
    }
);

Router::get('/bar',
    function ($request) {
        echo "I'll kill this request!";
        $request->end();
    },
    function ($request) {
        echo 'GET /bar'
    }
);
```
